---
title: "GDPR Compliance Guides"
description: "DSPM guides for GDPR compliance and data protection requirements."
layout: base.njk
regulation: "GDPR"
---

<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ regulation }} Compliance Guides</h1>
        <p>Comprehensive DSPM guides for {{ regulation }} compliance and data protection requirements.</p>
        <div class="badge regulation">{{ regulation }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Available Guides</h2>
        
        <div class="component-grid">
            {% for guide in collections.guides %}
            {% if guide.data.regulation == regulation and guide.data.status == 'published' %}
            <div class="component-card">
                <h4><a href="{{ guide.url }}" class="guide-link-title">{{ guide.data.title }}</a></h4>
                <p>{{ guide.data.description }}</p>
                <div class="guide-tags-container">
                    {% if guide.data.risk %}
                    <span class="guide-tag risk">{{ guide.data.risk }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                    <span class="guide-tag regulation">{{ guide.data.regulation }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">About GDPR</h2>
        <p>The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is a comprehensive data protection law that governs how organizations collect, process, and store personal data of EU residents. These guides help you implement the technical and organizational measures required for GDPR compliance in your data infrastructure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section next-steps">
        <h2 class="section-title">Related Resources</h2>
        <div>
            <a href="/" class="action-button">‚Üê Back to All Guides</a>
            <a href="/risk/data-exposure/" class="action-button">üéØ Browse by Risk Type</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>